<C>__{dignan}
<D>__{bob.}
<A>__{bob looks at dignan. dignan's looking across the room. there's future man and his friend clay fresh from a round of golf. they're standing on the other side of the room, looking across at bob. they're smiling. jackson picks up two empty plates and walks away. future man and clay walk to bob's table.}
